Name: hydrolethalus syndrome 1
Definition: A hydrolethalus syndrome that has_material_basis_in homozygous or compound heterozygous mutation in HYLS1 on chromosome 11q24.2.

Name: hydrolethalus syndrome 2
Definition: A hydrolethalus syndrome that has_material_basis_in homozygous or compound heterozygous mutation in KIF7 on chromosome 15q26.1.
